Class IndexedFieldValue<T extends DataObject,I extends DataObject>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.model.data.IndexedFieldValue<T,I>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of owning object
    I - type of remote object
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Accessor<IndexedReference<I>,T>, FilterProvider<T,IndexedReference<I>>, IndexedSQLValue<T,I>, SQLAccessor<IndexedReference<I>,T>, SQLValue<IndexedReference<I>>, FieldValue<IndexedReference<I>,T>, Selector, Targetted<IndexedReference<I>>

    public class IndexedFieldValue<T extends DataObject,I extends DataObject>
extends java.lang.Object
implements FieldValue<IndexedReference<I>,T>, IndexedSQLValue<T,I>, Selector
    A SQLAccessor for a field referencing a remote table. This accessor returns an IndexedReference for the remote object.
    Author:
    spb
